column16: Albert Pujols singles on a sharp ground ball to center fielder Carlos Gonzalez, deflected by shortstop Troy Tulowitzki.
Jon Jay grounds out, pitcher Edgar Gonzalez to first baseman Todd Helton.
Rafael Furcal flies out to center fielder Carlos Gonzalez.
Octavio Dotel grounds out to first baseman Todd Helton.
Skip Schumaker singles on a line drive to left fielder Eric Young.    David Freese scores.    Yadier Molina to 3rd.
Yadier Molina singles on a soft fly ball to right fielder Seth Smith.    Lance Berkman scores.    David Freese to 3rd.
David Freese walks.    Lance Berkman to 2nd.
Lance Berkman singles on a line drive to left fielder Eric Young.
Matt Holliday grounds into double play, shortstop Troy Tulowitzki to second baseman Mark Ellis to first baseman Todd Helton.    Albert Pujols out at 2nd.
